#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7582
msgid "``TOLERANCE``"
msgstr "``TOLERANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1765
msgid ""
"Specifies an optional snapping tolerance which can be used to improve the "
"robustness of the triangulation."
msgstr ""
"Zadaje opcionu toleranciju lepljenja koja se može koristiti za poboljšanje "
"robusnosti triangulacije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1766
msgid "**Add point IDs to output**"
msgstr "**Dodaj ID-jeve tačaka u izlaz**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1769
msgid "``ADD_ATTRIBUTES``"
msgstr "``ADD_ATTRIBUTES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1773
msgid ""
"Specifies whether fields storing involved point features ID should be added "
"to the output. If False, an ``id`` field is used to identify the polygons."
msgstr ""
"Zadaje da li treba dodati polja koja čuvaju ID uključenih tačkastih objekata"
" u izlaz. Ako je False, koristi se ``id`` polje za identifikaciju poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1775
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1799
msgid "**Delaunay triangulation**"
msgstr "**Delonijeva triangulacija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1802
msgid "The output (Delaunay triangulation) vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni (Delonijeva triangulacija) vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1807
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:delaunaytriangulation``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:delaunaytriangulation``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1817
msgid "Delete holes"
msgstr "Obriši rupe"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1818
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon layer and removes holes in polygons. It creates a new vector"
" layer in which polygons with holes have been replaced by polygons with only"
" their external ring. Attributes are not modified."
msgstr ""
"Uzima poligonski sloj i uklanja rupe u poligonima. Pravi novi vektorski sloj"
" u kojem su poligoni sa rupama zamenjeni poligonima sa samo njihovim "
"spoljašnjim prstenom. Atributi se ne menjaju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1823
msgid ""
"An optional minimum area parameter allows removing only holes which are "
"smaller than a specified area threshold. Leaving this parameter at ``0.0`` "
"results in all holes being removed."
msgstr ""
"Opcioni parametar minimalne površine omogućava uklanjanje samo rupa koje su "
"manje od zadatog praga površine. Ostavljanje ovog parametra na ``0.0`` daje "
"uklanjanje svih rupa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1830
msgid "Before and after the cleaning"
msgstr "Pre i posle čišćenja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1836
msgid "qgisfixgeometryhole"
msgstr "qgisfixgeometryhole"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1853
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2438
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3727
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5115
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7213
msgid "Input polygon vector layer"
msgstr "Ulazni poligonski vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1854
msgid "**Remove holes with area less than**"
msgstr "**Ukloni rupe sa površinom manjom od**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1857
msgid "``MIN_AREA``"
msgstr "``MIN_AREA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1861
msgid ""
"Only holes with an area less than this threshold will be deleted. With a "
"value of ``0.0``, **all** the holes will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Biće obrisane samo rupe sa površinom manjom od ovog praga. Sa vrednošću "
"``0.0``, biće obrisane **sve** rupe."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1864
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1887
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5470
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5493
msgid "**Cleaned**"
msgstr "**Očišćeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1890
msgid "The output (cleaned) vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni (očišćeni) vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1895
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:deleteholes``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:deleteholes``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1905
msgid "Densify by count"
msgstr "Zgusni po broju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1906
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1992
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon or line layer and generates a new one in which the "
"geometries have a larger number of vertices than the original one."
msgstr ""
"Uzima poligonski ili linijski sloj i generiše novi u kojem geometrije imaju "
"veći broj temena od originalnog."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1909
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1999
msgid ""
"If the geometries have Z or M values present then these will be linearly "
"interpolated at the added vertices."
msgstr ""
"Ako su Z ili M vrednosti prisutne u geometrijama, one će biti linearno "
"interpolirane na dodatim temenima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1912
msgid ""
"The number of new vertices to add to each segment is specified as an input "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"Broj novih temena koja se dodaju svakom segmentu zadaje se kao ulazni "
"parametar."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1918
msgid "Red points show the vertices before and after the densify"
msgstr "Crvene tačke prikazuju temena pre i posle zgušnjavanja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1926
msgid ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1944
msgid "**Vertices to add**"
msgstr "**Temena za dodavanje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1945
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2814
msgid "``VERTICES``"
msgstr "``VERTICES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1948
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2266
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3310
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3732
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4233
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6119
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6551
msgid "Default: 1"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1949
msgid "Number of vertices to add to each segment"
msgstr "Broj temena koja se dodaju svakom segmentu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1950
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1973
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2043
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2066
msgid "**Densified**"
msgstr "**Zgusnuto**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1976
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2069
msgid "The output (densified) vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni (zgusnuti) vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1981
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometries``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:densifygeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1991
msgid "Densify by interval"
msgstr "Zgusni po intervalu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1995
msgid ""
"The geometries are densified by adding regularly placed extra vertices "
"inside each segment so that the maximum distance between any two vertices "
"does not exceed the specified distance."
msgstr ""
"Geometrije se zgušnjavaju dodavanjem pravilno raspoređenih dodatnih temena "
"unutar svakog segmenta tako da maksimalno rastojanje između bilo koja dva "
"temena ne prelazi zadato rastojanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2002
msgid "**Example**"
msgstr "**Primer**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2004
msgid ""
"Specifying a distance of 3 would cause the segment ``[0 0] -> [10 0]`` to be"
" converted to ``[0 0] -> [2.5 0] -> [5 0] -> [7.5 0] -> [10 0]``, since 3 "
"extra vertices are required on the segment and spacing these at 2.5 "
"increments allows them to be evenly spaced over the segment."
msgstr ""
"Zadavanje rastojanja od 3 uzrokovalo bi da se segment ``[0 0] -> [10 0]`` "
"pretvori u ``[0 0] -> [2.5 0] -> [5 0] -> [7.5 0] -> [10 0]``, pošto su na "
"segmentu potrebna 3 dodatna temena, a njihovo raspoređivanje u koracima od "
"2.5 omogućava im da budu ravnomerno raspoređena preko segmenta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2013
msgid "Densify geometry at a given interval"
msgstr "Zgušnjavanje geometrije na zadatom intervalu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2019
msgid ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometries`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometries`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2037
msgid "**Interval between vertices to add**"
msgstr "**Interval između temena za dodavanje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2038
msgid "``INTERVAL``"
msgstr "``INTERVAL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2042
msgid "Maximum distance between two consecutive vertices"
msgstr "Maksimalno rastojanje između dva uzastopna temena"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2074
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometriesgivenaninterval``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:densifygeometriesgivenaninterval``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2084
msgid "Dissolve"
msgstr "Stapanje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2085
msgid ""
"Takes a vector layer and combines its features into new features. One or "
"more attributes can be specified to dissolve features belonging to the same "
"class (having the same value for the specified attributes), alternatively "
"all features can be dissolved to a single feature."
msgstr ""
"Uzima vektorski sloj i kombinuje njegove objekte u nove objekte. Može se "
"zadati jedan ili više atributa da bi se stopili objekti koji pripadaju istoj"
" klasi (imaju istu vrednost za zadate atribute), ili se alternativno svi "
"objekti mogu stopiti u jedan objekat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2091
msgid ""
"All output geometries will be converted to multi geometries. In case the "
"input is a polygon layer, common boundaries of adjacent polygons being "
"dissolved will get erased. If enabled, the optional \"Keep disjoint features"
" separate\" setting will cause features and parts that do not overlap or "
"touch to be exported as separate features (instead of parts of a single "
"multipart feature)."
msgstr ""
"Sve izlazne geometrije biće pretvorene u višedelne geometrije. U slučaju da "
"je ulaz poligonski sloj, zajedničke granice susednih poligona koji se "
"stapaju biće izbrisane. Ako je omogućeno, opciono podešavanje „Zadrži "
"razdvojene objekte odvojenima“ uzrokovaće da objekti i delovi koji se ne "
"preklapaju niti dodiruju budu izvezeni kao odvojeni objekti (umesto delova "
"jednog višedelnog objekta)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2098
msgid ""
"The resulting attribute table will have the same fields as the input layer. "
"The values in the output layer's fields are the ones of the first input "
"feature that happens to be processed."
msgstr ""
"Rezultujuća atributska tabela imaće ista polja kao ulazni sloj. Vrednosti u "
"poljima izlaznog sloja su one prvog ulaznog objekta koji se obradi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2107
msgid "Dissolving a layer into a single multipart feature"
msgstr "Stapanje sloja u jedan višedelni objekat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2114
msgid ":ref:`qgiscoverageunion`, :ref:`qgisaggregate`, :ref:`qgiscollect`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgiscoverageunion`, :ref:`qgisaggregate`, :ref:`qgiscollect`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2135
msgid "**Dissolve field(s)**"
msgstr "**Polja za stapanje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2141
msgid "Default: []"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: []"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2142
msgid ""
"Features having the same value for the selected field(s) will be replaced "
"with a single one and their geometries are merged."
msgstr ""
"Objekti koji imaju istu vrednost za izabrano polje(a) biće zamenjeni jednim,"
" a njihove geometrije se spajaju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2146
msgid ""
"If no field is provided then all the features are dissolved, resulting in a "
"single (multipart) feature."
msgstr ""
"Ako se ne zada nijedno polje, tada se svi objekti stapaju, dajući jedan "
"(višedelni) objekat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2153
msgid ""
"Dissolve the polygon layer on a common attribute (2 multipart features)"
msgstr ""
"Stapanje poligonskog sloja po zajedničkom atributu (2 višedelna objekta)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2155
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2208
msgid "**Dissolved**"
msgstr "**Stopljeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2183
msgid ""
"Parts of dissolved features are exported as separate features (instead of "
"parts of a multipart feature)."
msgstr ""
"Delovi stopljenih objekata izvoze se kao odvojeni objekti (umesto delova "
"višedelnog objekta)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2189
msgid "source (left), dissolve all (3 distinct features - right)"
msgstr "izvor (levo), stopi sve (3 različita objekta - desno)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2194
msgid "source (left), dissolve on field (5 distinct features - right)"
msgstr "izvor (levo), stopi po polju (5 različitih objekata - desno)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2211
msgid "The output vector layer with dissolved geometries"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa stopljenim geometrijama"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2216
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:dissolve``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:dissolve``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2226
msgid "Drape (set Z value from raster)"
msgstr "Prekri (postavi Z vrednost iz rastera)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2227
msgid ""
"Uses values sampled from a band within a raster layer to set the Z value for"
" every overlapping vertex in the feature geometry. The raster values can "
"optionally be scaled by a preset amount."
msgstr ""
"Koristi vrednosti uzorkovane iz kanala unutar rasterskog sloja za "
"postavljanje Z vrednosti za svako preklapajuće teme u geometriji objekta. "
"Vrednosti rastera se opciono mogu skalirati unapred zadatim iznosom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2231
msgid ""
"If Z values already exist in the layer, they will be overwritten with the "
"new value. If no Z values exist, the geometry will be upgraded to include "
"the Z dimension."
msgstr ""
"Ako Z vrednosti već postoje u sloju, biće prepisane novom vrednošću. Ako Z "
"vrednosti ne postoje, geometrija će biti unapređena da uključi Z dimenziju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2236
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6192
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line, and polygon features with Z "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste, linijske i poligonske objekte sa "
"omogućenim Z"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2240
msgid ":ref:`qgissetmfromraster`, :ref:`qgissetzvalue`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgissetmfromraster`, :ref:`qgissetzvalue`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2258
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6111
