msgstr "``OFFSET``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2287
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6139
msgid ""
"Offset value: it is algebraically added to the band values after applying "
"the \"Scale factor\"."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost pomeraja: algebarski se dodaje vrednostima kanala nakon primene "
"„Faktora skaliranja“."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2289
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2313
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6141
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6165
msgid "**Updated**"
msgstr "**Ažurirano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2294
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer (with Z values from the raster layer). "
":ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj (sa Z vrednostima iz rasterskog sloja). "
":ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2316
msgid "The output vector layer with Z values from the raster layer"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa Z vrednostima iz rasterskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2322
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:setzfromraster``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:setzfromraster``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2332
msgid "Drop M/Z values"
msgstr "Odbaci M/Z vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2333
