"Uzima vektorski sloj i generiše tačkasti sloj sa tačkama koje predstavljaju "
"određena temena u ulaznim geometrijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2769
msgid ""
"For instance, this algorithm can be used to extract the first or last "
"vertices in the geometry. The attributes associated to each point are the "
"same ones associated to the feature that the vertex belongs to."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, ovaj algoritam se može koristiti za izdvajanje prvog ili "
"poslednjeg temena u geometriji. Atributi povezani sa svakom tačkom isti su "
"kao oni povezani sa objektom kojem teme pripada."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2774
msgid ""
"The vertex indices parameter accepts a comma separated string specifying the"
" indices of the vertices to extract. The first vertex corresponds to an "
"index of 0, the second vertex has an index of 1, etc. Negative indices can "
"be used to find vertices at the end of the geometry, e.g., an index of -1 "
"corresponds to the last vertex, -2 corresponds to the second last vertex, "
"etc."
msgstr ""
"Parametar indeksa temena prihvata nisku razdvojenu zarezima koja zadaje "
"indekse temena za izdvajanje. Prvom temenu odgovara indeks 0, drugo teme ima"
" indeks 1, itd. Negativni indeksi se mogu koristiti za pronalaženje temena "
"na kraju geometrije, npr. indeks -1 odgovara poslednjem temenu, -2 odgovara "
"pretposlednjem temenu, itd."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2781
msgid ""
"Additional fields are added to the vertices indicating the specific vertex "
"position (e.g., 0, -1, etc), the original vertex index, the vertex’s part "
"and its index within the part (as well as its ring for polygons), distance "
"along the original geometry and bisector angle of vertex for the original "
"geometry."
msgstr ""
"Temenima se dodaju dodatna polja koja označavaju određeni položaj temena "
"(npr. 0, -1, itd.), originalni indeks temena, deo temena i njegov indeks "
"unutar dela (kao i njegov prsten za poligone), rastojanje duž originalne "
"geometrije i ugao simetrale temena za originalnu geometriju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2794
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisextractvertices`, :ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, "
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisextractvertices`, :ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, "
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2813
msgid "**Vertex indices**"
msgstr "**Indeksi temena**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2817
msgid "Default: '0'"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: '0'"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2818
msgid "Comma-separated string of the indices of the vertices to extract."
msgstr "Niska razdvojena zarezima indeksa temena za izdvajanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2820
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2843
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2917
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2940
msgid "**Vertices**"
msgstr "**Temena**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2846
msgid ""
"The output (point) vector layer containing the specified vertices from the "
"input layer geometries. Other than the input attributes, the output layer "
"also contains the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni (tačkasti) vektorski sloj koji sadrži zadata temena iz geometrija "
"ulaznog sloja. Pored ulaznih atributa, izlazni sloj takođe sadrži sledeća "
"polja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2850
msgid ""
"``vertex_pos``: the index of the vertex in the geometry, as requested by the"
" user."
msgstr ""
"``vertex_pos``: indeks temena u geometriji, kako je zatražio korisnik."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2851
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2947
msgid ""
"``vertex_index``: the index of the vertex within the geometry. The first "
"vertex is indexed as 0."
msgstr ""
"``vertex_index``: indeks temena unutar geometrije. Prvo teme je indeksirano "
"kao 0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2852
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2948
msgid ""
"``vertex_part``: the part number of the geometry that the vertex belongs to."
" For single-part geometries, this is always 0. For multi-part geometries "
"(e.g. MultiPolygon or MultiLine), this indicates which part the vertex comes"
" from."
msgstr ""
"``vertex_part``: broj dela geometrije kojem teme pripada. Za jednodelne "
"geometrije, ovo je uvek 0. Za višedelne geometrije (npr. MultiPolygon ili "
"MultiLine), ovo označava iz kog dela teme potiče."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2854
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2950
msgid ""
"``vertex_part_ring``: for polygon geometries, this indicates whether the "
"vertex belongs to the outer ring (0) or one of the inner rings (1, 2, ...)."
msgstr ""
"``vertex_part_ring``: za geometrije poligona, ovo označava da li teme "
"pripada spoljašnjem prstenu (0) ili jednom od unutrašnjih prstenova (1, 2, "
"...)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2855
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2951
msgid ""
"``vertex_part_index``: the index of the vertex in its specific ring (outer "
"or inner)."
msgstr ""
"``vertex_part_index``: indeks temena u njegovom određenom prstenu "
"(spoljašnjem ili unutrašnjem)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2856
msgid ""
"``distance``: the cumulative length of line segments from the first vertex "
"of the geometry."
msgstr ""
"``distance``: kumulativna dužina segmenata linije od prvog temena "
"geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2857
msgid ""
"``angle``: the angle (in degrees) between the previous and the current "
"vertex."
msgstr "``angle``: ugao (u stepenima) između prethodnog i trenutnog temena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2862
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:extractspecificvertices``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:extractspecificvertices``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2872
msgid "Extract vertices"
msgstr "Izdvoj temena"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2873
msgid ""
"Takes a vector layer and generates a point layer with points representing "
"the vertices in the input geometries."
msgstr ""
"Uzima vektorski sloj i generiše tačkasti sloj sa tačkama koje predstavljaju "
"temena u ulaznim geometrijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2876
msgid ""
"The attributes associated to each point are the same ones associated to the "
"feature that the vertex belongs to."
msgstr ""
"Atributi povezani sa svakom tačkom isti su kao oni povezani sa objektom "
"kojem teme pripada."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2879
msgid ""
"Additional fields are added to the vertices indicating the vertex index "
"(beginning at 0), the feature’s part and its index within the part (as well "
"as its ring for polygons), distance along original geometry and bisector "
"angle of vertex for original geometry."
msgstr ""
"Temenima se dodaju dodatna polja koja označavaju indeks temena (počev od 0),"
" deo objekta i njegov indeks unutar dela (kao i njegov prsten za poligone), "
"rastojanje duž originalne geometrije i ugao simetrale temena za originalnu "
"geometriju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2887
msgid "Vertices extracted for line and polygon layer"
msgstr "Temena izdvojena za linijski i poligonski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2898
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`, :ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, "
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`, :ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, "
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2943
msgid ""
"The output (point) vector layer containing the vertices from the input layer"
" geometries. Other than the input attributes, the output layer also contains"
" the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni (tačkasti) vektorski sloj koji sadrži temena iz geometrija ulaznog "
"sloja. Pored ulaznih atributa, izlazni sloj takođe sadrži sledeća polja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2952
msgid "``distance``: the distance from the previous vertex."
msgstr "``distance``: rastojanje od prethodnog temena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2953
msgid ""
"``angle``: returns approximate angle at a vertex. Usually the average angle "
"between adjacent segments, and can be pictured as the orientation of a line "
"following the curvature of the geometry at the specified vertex."
msgstr ""
"``angle``: vraća približan ugao na temenu. Obično prosečan ugao između "
"susednih segmenata, i može se zamisliti kao orijentacija linije koja prati "
"zakrivljenost geometrije na zadatom temenu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2961
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:extractvertices``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:extractvertices``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2971
msgid "Extract Z values"
msgstr "Izdvoj Z vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2973
msgid "Extracts Z values from geometries into feature attributes."
msgstr "Izdvaja Z vrednosti iz geometrija u atribute objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2975
msgid ""
"By default only the Z value from the first vertex of each feature is "
"extracted, however the algorithm can optionally calculate statistics on all "
"of the geometry's Z values, including sum, mean, minimum and maximum."
msgstr ""
"Podrazumevano se izdvaja samo Z vrednost iz prvog temena svakog objekta, "
"međutim algoritam može opciono izračunati statistiku na svim Z vrednostima "
"geometrije, uključujući zbir, srednju vrednost, minimum i maksimum."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2980
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisextractmvalues`, :ref:`qgissetzvalue`, :ref:`qgisdropmzvalues`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisextractmvalues`, :ref:`qgissetzvalue`, :ref:`qgisdropmzvalues`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3004
msgid "Statistics on the Z values of a geometry. One or more of:"
msgstr "Statistika na Z vrednostima geometrije. Jedno ili više od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3028
msgid "Default: 'z\\_'"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 'z\\_'"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3029
msgid "The prefix for the output (Z) column"
msgstr "Prefiks za izlaznu (Z) kolonu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3057
msgid "The output vector layer (with Z values)"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj (sa Z vrednostima)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3062
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:extractzvalues``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:extractzvalues``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3072
msgid "Filter vertices by M value"
msgstr "Filtriraj temena po M vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3073
msgid ""
"Filters away vertices based on their M value, returning geometries with only"
" vertex points that have a M value greater than or equal to the specified "
"minimum value and/or less than or equal to the maximum value."
msgstr ""
"Filtrira temena na osnovu njihove M vrednosti, vraćajući geometrije sa samo "
"onim temenima koja imaju M vrednost veću od ili jednaku zadatoj minimalnoj "
"vrednosti i/ili manju od ili jednaku maksimalnoj vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3078
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3179
msgid ""
"If the minimum value is not specified then only the maximum value is tested,"
" and similarly if the maximum value is not specified then only the minimum "
"value is tested."
msgstr ""
"Ako minimalna vrednost nije zadata, tada se proverava samo maksimalna "
"vrednost, i slično, ako maksimalna vrednost nije zadata, tada se proverava "
"samo minimalna vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3085
msgid ""
"The red line represents the black line with only vertices whose M value is "
"<=10."
msgstr ""
"Crvena linija predstavlja crnu liniju sa samo onim temenima čija je M "
"vrednost <=10."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3088
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line and polygon features with M "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste, linijske i poligonske objekte sa "
"omogućenim M"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3092
msgid ""
"Depending on the input geometry attributes and the filters used, the "
"geometries created by this algorithm may no longer be valid."
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od atributa ulazne geometrije i korišćenih filtera, geometrije "
"napravljene ovim algoritmom možda više neće biti validne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3095
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbyz`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3113
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3216
msgid "Input vector layer to remove vertices from"
msgstr "Ulazni vektorski sloj iz kojeg se uklanjaju temena"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3115
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3218
msgid "**Minimum**"
msgstr "**Minimum**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3118
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3221
msgid "``MIN``"
msgstr "``MIN``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3122
msgid "Minimum of M values allowed"
msgstr "Minimum dozvoljenih M vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3123
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3226
msgid "**Maximum**"
msgstr "**Maksimum**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3126
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3229
msgid "``MAX``"
msgstr "``MAX``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3130
msgid "Maximum of M values allowed"
msgstr "Maksimum dozvoljenih M vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3131
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3154
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3234
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3257
msgid "**Filtered**"
msgstr "**Filtrirano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3157
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3260
msgid "The output vector layer of features with only the filtered vertices."
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj objekata sa samo filtriranim temenima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3163
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:filterverticesbym``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:filterverticesbym``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3173
msgid "Filter vertices by Z value"
msgstr "Filtriraj temena po Z vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3174
msgid ""
"Filters away vertices based on their Z value, returning geometries with only"
" vertex points that have a Z value greater than or equal to the specified "
"minimum value and/or less than or equal to the maximum value."
msgstr ""
"Filtrira temena na osnovu njihove Z vrednosti, vraćajući geometrije sa samo "
"onim temenima koja imaju Z vrednost veću od ili jednaku zadatoj minimalnoj "
"vrednosti i/ili manju od ili jednaku maksimalnoj vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3186
msgid ""
"The red line represents the black line with only vertices whose Z value is "
"<=10."
msgstr ""
"Crvena linija predstavlja crnu liniju sa samo onim temenima čija je Z "
"vrednost <=10."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3189
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line and polygon features with Z "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste, linijske i poligonske objekte sa "
"omogućenim Z"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3193
msgid ""
"Depending on the input geometry attributes and the filters used, the "
"geometries created by this algorithm may no longer be valid. You may need to"
" run the :ref:`qgisfixgeometries` algorithm to ensure their validity."
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od atributa ulazne geometrije i korišćenih filtera, geometrije "
"napravljene ovim algoritmom možda više neće biti validne. Možda ćete morati "
"da pokrenete algoritam :ref:`qgisfixgeometries` da biste obezbedili njihovu "
"validnost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3198
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3225
msgid "Minimum of Z values allowed"
msgstr "Minimum dozvoljenih Z vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3233
msgid "Maximum of Z values allowed"
msgstr "Maksimum dozvoljenih Z vrednosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3266
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:filterverticesbyz``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:filterverticesbyz``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3276
msgid "Fix geometries"
msgstr "Popravi geometrije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3277
msgid ""
"Attempts to create a valid representation of a given invalid geometry "
"without losing any of the input vertices. Already valid geometries are "
"returned without further intervention. Always outputs multi-geometry layer."
msgstr ""
"Pokušava da napravi validnu reprezentaciju zadate nevažeće geometrije bez "
"gubljenja bilo kog ulaznog temena. Već validne geometrije se vraćaju bez "
"daljeg mešanja. Uvek daje sloj sa višestrukom geometrijom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3282
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line, and polygon features without M "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste, linijske i poligonske objekte bez "
"omogućenog M"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3286
msgid "M values will be dropped from the output."
msgstr "M vrednosti će biti odbačene iz izlaza."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3288
msgid ":ref:`qgischeckvalidity`, :ref:`fixgeometry_algorithms`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgischeckvalidity`, :ref:`fixgeometry_algorithms`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3306
msgid "**Repair method**"
msgstr "**Metod popravke**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3311
msgid "Method used to repair the geometries. One of:"
msgstr "Metod koji se koristi za popravku geometrija. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3313
msgid ""
"0 --- ``Linework``: combines all rings into a set of noded lines and then "
"extracts valid polygons from that linework"
msgstr ""
"0 --- ``Linework``: kombinuje sve prstenove u skup povezanih linija, a zatim"
" iz te linijske mreže izdvaja validne poligone"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3315
msgid ""
"1 --- ``Structure``: first makes all rings valid and then merges shells and "
"subtracts holes from shells to generate valid result. Assumes that holes and"
" shells are correctly categorized."
msgstr ""
"1 --- ``Structure``: prvo čini sve prstenove validnim, a zatim spaja ljuske "
"i oduzima rupe od ljuski da bi generisao validan rezultat. Pretpostavlja da "
"su rupe i ljuske ispravno kategorizovane."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3319
msgid ""
"Using this method requires QGIS installed with GEOS_ >= 3.10 (see "
":menuselection:`Help --> About` menu)."
msgstr ""
"Korišćenje ovog metoda zahteva QGIS instaliran sa GEOS_ >= 3.10 (pogledajte "
"meni :menuselection:`Pomoć --> O programu`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3322
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3345
msgid "**Fixed geometries**"
msgstr "**Popravljene geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3348
msgid "The output vector layer with fixed geometries."
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa popravljenim geometrijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3353
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:fixgeometries``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:fixgeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3363
msgid "Force right-hand-rule"
msgstr "Nametni pravilo desne ruke"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3365
msgid ""
"Forces polygon geometries to respect the Right-Hand-Rule, in which the area "
"that is bounded by a polygon is to the right of the boundary. In particular,"
" the exterior ring is oriented in a clockwise direction and any interior "
"rings in a counter-clockwise direction."
msgstr ""
"Prisiljava geometrije poligona da poštuju pravilo desne ruke, u kojem je "
"površina omeđena poligonom sa desne strane granice. Naročito, spoljašnji "
"prsten je orijentisan u smeru kazaljke na satu, a bilo koji unutrašnji "
"prstenovi suprotno od kazaljke na satu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3390
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3413
msgid "**Reoriented**"
msgstr "**Preorijentisano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3416
msgid "The output vector layer with reoriented geometries."
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa preorijentisanim geometrijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3421
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:forcerhr``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:forcerhr``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3431
msgid "Geodesic line split at antimeridian"
msgstr "Geodetsko deljenje linije na antimeridijanu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3433
msgid ""
"Splits a line into multiple geodesic segments, whenever the line crosses the"
" antimeridian (±180 degrees longitude)."
msgstr ""
"Deli liniju na više geodetskih segmenata, svaki put kada linija pređe "
"antimeridijan (±180 stepeni geografske dužine)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3436
msgid ""
"Splitting at the antimeridian helps the visual display of the lines in some "
"projections. The returned geometry will always be a multi-part geometry."
msgstr ""
"Deljenje na antimeridijanu pomaže vizuelnom prikazu linija u nekim "
"projekcijama. Vraćena geometrija će uvek biti višedelna geometrija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3440
msgid ""
"Whenever line segments in the input geometry cross the antimeridian, they "
"will be split into two segments, with the latitude of the breakpoint being "
"determined using a geodesic line connecting the points either side of this "
"segment. The current project ellipsoid setting will be used when calculating"
" this breakpoint."
msgstr ""
"Svaki put kada segmenti linije u ulaznoj geometriji pređu antimeridijan, "
"biće podeljeni na dva segmenta, sa geografskom širinom tačke preloma "
"određenom pomoću geodetske linije koja povezuje tačke sa obe strane tog "
"segmenta. Pri računanju ove tačke preloma koristiće se trenutno podešavanje "
"elipsoida projekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3447
msgid ""
"If the input geometry contains M or Z values, these will be linearly "
"interpolated for the new vertices created at the antimeridian."
msgstr ""
"Ako ulazna geometrija sadrži M ili Z vrednosti, one će biti linearno "
"interpolirane za nova temena napravljena na antimeridijanu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3473
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3496
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6879
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6904
msgid "**Split**"
msgstr "**Podeljeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3478
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3831
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3968
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5121
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5641
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6884
msgid ""
"Specify the output line vector layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni linijski vektorski sloj. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3499
msgid "The output line vector layer split at the antimeridian."
msgstr "Izlazni linijski vektorski sloj podeljen na antimeridijanu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3504
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:antimeridiansplit``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:antimeridiansplit``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3514
msgid "Geometry by expression"
msgstr "Geometrija pomoću izraza"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3515
msgid ""
"Updates existing geometries (or creates new geometries) for input features "
"by use of a QGIS expression."
msgstr ""
"Ažurira postojeće geometrije (ili pravi nove geometrije) za ulazne objekte "
"korišćenjem QGIS izraza."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3518
msgid ""
"This allows complex geometry modifications which can utilize all the "
"flexibility of the QGIS expression engine to manipulate and create "
"geometries for output features."
msgstr ""
"Ovo omogućava složene izmene geometrije koje mogu iskoristiti svu "
"fleksibilnost mehanizma za izraze QGIS-a za manipulaciju i pravljenje "
"geometrija za izlazne objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3522
msgid ""
"For help with QGIS expression functions, see the inbuilt help available in "
"the :ref:`expression builder <vector_expressions>`."
msgstr ""
"Za pomoć sa funkcijama QGIS izraza, pogledajte ugrađenu pomoć dostupnu u "
":ref:`graditelju izraza <vector_expressions>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3541
msgid "**Output geometry type**"
msgstr "**Izlazni tip geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3542
msgid "``OUTPUT_GEOMETRY``"
msgstr "``OUTPUT_GEOMETRY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3546
msgid ""
"The output geometry strongly depends on the expression: for instance, if you"
" create a buffer the geometry type has to be polygon. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Izlazna geometrija u velikoj meri zavisi od izraza: na primer, ako napravite"
" bafer, tip geometrije mora biti poligon. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3551
msgid "0 --- Polygon"
msgstr "0 --- Poligon"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3552
msgid "1 --- Line"
msgstr "1 --- Linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3553
msgid "2 --- Point"
msgstr "2 --- Tačka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3555
msgid "**Output geometry has z values**"
msgstr "**Izlazna geometrija ima z vrednosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3556
msgid "``WITH_Z``"
msgstr "``WITH_Z``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3560
msgid "Choose if the output geometry should include the Z dimension"
msgstr "Izaberite da li izlazna geometrija treba da uključuje Z dimenziju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3561
msgid "**Output geometry has m values**"
msgstr "**Izlazna geometrija ima m vrednosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3562
msgid "``WITH_M``"
msgstr "``WITH_M``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3566
msgid "Choose if the output geometry should include the M dimension"
msgstr "Izaberite da li izlazna geometrija treba da uključuje M dimenziju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3567
msgid "**Geometry expression**"
msgstr "**Izraz geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3568
msgid "``EXPRESSION``"
msgstr "``EXPRESSION``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3569
msgid "[expression]"
msgstr "[izraz]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3571
msgid "Default: '$geometry'"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: '$geometry'"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3572
msgid ""
"Add the geometry expression you want to use. You can use the button to open "
"the Expression Dialog. The dialog lists all the relevant expressions, "
"together with their help and guide."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte izraz geometrije koji želite da koristite. Možete koristiti dugme za"
" otvaranje dijaloga izraza. Dijalog navodi sve relevantne izraze, zajedno sa"
" njihovom pomoći i vodičem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3576
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3599
msgid "**Modified geometry**"
msgstr "**Izmenjena geometrija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3602
msgid "The output vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3607
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:geometrybyexpression``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:geometrybyexpression``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3617
msgid "Interpolate point on line"
msgstr "Interpoliraj tačku na liniji"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3618
msgid ""
"Creates a point geometry interpolated at a set distance along line or curve "
"geometries."
msgstr ""
"Pravi geometriju tačke interpoliranu na zadatom rastojanju duž geometrija "
"linije ili krive."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3621
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3782
msgid "Z and M values are linearly interpolated from existing values."
msgstr "Z i M vrednosti se linearno interpoliraju iz postojećih vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3623
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3784
msgid ""
"If a multipart geometry is encountered, only the first part is considered "
"when calculating the substring."
msgstr ""
"Ako se naiđe na višedelnu geometriju, samo se prvi deo uzima u obzir pri "
"računanju podniske."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3626
msgid ""
"If the specified distance is greater than the input feature's length, the "
"resultant feature will have a null geometry."
msgstr ""
"Ako je zadato rastojanje veće od dužine ulaznog objekta, rezultujući objekat"
" imaće nultu geometriju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3632
msgid "Interpolated point at 500m of the beginning of the line"
msgstr "Interpolirana tačka na 500 m od početka linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3634
msgid ":ref:`qgispointsalonglines`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgispointsalonglines`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3657
msgid "Distance from the beginning of the line"
msgstr "Rastojanje od početka linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3658
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3681
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4796
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4819
msgid "**Interpolated points**"
msgstr "**Interpolirane tačke**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3684
msgid ""
"The output point vector layer with features at a set distance along the line"
" or polygon boundary"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj sa objektima na zadatom rastojanju duž "
"linije ili granice poligona"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3690
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:interpolatepoint``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:interpolatepoint``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3700
msgid "Keep N biggest parts"
msgstr "Zadrži N najvećih delova"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3701
msgid ""
"Takes a layer with polygons or multipolygons and returns a new layer in "
"which only the *n* largest polygons of each multipolygon feature are kept. "
"If a feature has *n* or fewer parts, the feature will just be copied."
msgstr ""
"Uzima sloj sa poligonima ili multipoligonima i vraća novi sloj u kojem se "
"zadržava samo *n* najvećih poligona svakog multipoligonskog objekta. Ako "
"objekat ima *n* ili manje delova, objekat će jednostavno biti kopiran."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3709
msgid ""
"Clockwise from top left: original multipart feature, one, two and three "
"biggest parts kept"
msgstr ""
"U smeru kazaljke na satu od gornjeg levog: originalni višedelni objekat, "
"jedan, dva i tri najveća dela zadržana"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3724
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3894
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3917
msgid "**Polygons**"
msgstr "**Poligoni**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3728
msgid "**Parts to keep**"
msgstr "**Delovi za zadržavanje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3729
msgid "``PARTS``"
msgstr "``PARTS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3730
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4231
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6549
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6969
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7134
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7490
msgid "[numeric: integer] |dataDefine|"
msgstr "[numerički: ceo broj] |dataDefine|"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3733
msgid ""
"Number of parts to keep. If 1, only the biggest part of the feature will be "
"kept."
msgstr ""
"Broj delova za zadržavanje. Ako je 1, zadržaće se samo najveći deo objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3735
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3758
msgid "**Parts**"
msgstr "**Delovi**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3740
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3899
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4068
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4155
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4252
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4335
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4535
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4630
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4968
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5047
msgid ""
"Specify the output polygon vector layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3761
msgid ""
"The output polygon vector layer with the N biggest parts of each feature"
msgstr "Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj sa N najvećih delova svakog objekta"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3767
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:keepnbiggestparts``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:keepnbiggestparts``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3777
msgid "Line substring"
msgstr "Podniska linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3778
msgid ""
"Returns the portion of a line (or curve) which falls between the specified "
"start and end distances (measured from the beginning of the line)."
msgstr ""
"Vraća deo linije (ili krive) koji pada između zadatih početnog i krajnjeg "
"rastojanja (mereno od početka linije)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3790
msgid ""
"Substring line with starting distance set at 0 meters and the ending "
"distance at 250 meters."
msgstr ""
"Podniska linije sa početnim rastojanjem postavljenim na 0 metara i krajnjim "
"rastojanjem na 250 metara."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3796
msgid ":ref:`qgisextendlines`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisextendlines`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3819
msgid "Distance along the input line to the start point of the output feature"
msgstr "Rastojanje duž ulazne linije do početne tačke izlaznog objekta"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3825
msgid "Distance along the input line to the end point of the output feature"
msgstr "Rastojanje duž ulazne linije do krajnje tačke izlaznog objekta"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3826
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3849
msgid "**Substring**"
msgstr "**Podniska**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3852
msgid "The output line vector layer."
msgstr "Izlazni linijski vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3857
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:linesubstring``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:linesubstring``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3867
msgid "Lines to polygons"
msgstr "Linije u poligone"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3868
msgid ""
"Generates a polygon layer using as polygon rings the lines from an input "
"line layer."
msgstr ""
"Generiše poligonski sloj koristeći kao prstenove poligona linije iz ulaznog "
"linijskog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3876
msgid ""
":ref:`qgispolygonstolines`, :ref:`qgispolygonize`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgispolygonstolines`, :ref:`qgispolygonize`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3925
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:linestopolygons``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:linestopolygons``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3935
msgid "Merge lines"
msgstr "Spoji linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3936
msgid ""
"Joins all connected parts of MultiLineString geometries into single "
"LineString geometries."
msgstr ""
"Spaja sve povezane delove MultiLineString geometrija u pojedinačne "
"LineString geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3939
msgid ""
"If any parts of the input MultiLineString geometries are not connected, the "
"resultant geometry will be a MultiLineString containing any lines which "
"could be merged and any non-connected line parts."
msgstr ""
"Ako bilo koji delovi ulaznih MultiLineString geometrija nisu povezani, "
"rezultujuća geometrija biće MultiLineString koji sadrži sve linije koje su "
"mogle biti spojene i sve nepovezane delove linija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3963
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3986
msgid "**Merged**"
msgstr "**Spojeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3989
msgid "The output (merged) line vector layer."
msgstr "Izlazni (spojeni) linijski vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3994
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:mergelines``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:mergelines``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4004
msgid "Minimum bounding geometry"
msgstr "Minimalna granična geometrija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4005
msgid ""
"Creates geometries which enclose the features from an input layer. The "
"features can be grouped by a field. The output layer will then contain one "
"feature per group value with a geometry (MBB) that covers the geometries of "
"the features with matching value."
msgstr ""
"Pravi geometrije koje obuhvataju objekte iz ulaznog sloja. Objekti se mogu "
"grupisati po polju. Izlazni sloj će tada sadržati po jedan objekat po "
"vrednosti grupe sa geometrijom (MBB) koja pokriva geometrije objekata sa "
"odgovarajućom vrednošću."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4011
msgid "The following enclosing geometry types are supported:"
msgstr "Podržani su sledeći tipovi obuhvatajuće geometrije:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4013
msgid "bounding box (envelope)"
msgstr "granični pravougaonik (omotnica)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4014
msgid "oriented rectangle"
msgstr "orijentisani pravougaonik"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4015
msgid "circle"
msgstr "krug"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4016
msgid "convex hull"
msgstr "konveksni omotač"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4021
msgid ""
"Clockwise from top left: envelope, oriented rectangle, circle, convex hull"
msgstr ""
"U smeru kazaljke na satu od gornjeg levog: omotnica, orijentisani "
"pravougaonik, krug, konveksni omotač"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4024
msgid ":ref:`qgisminimumenclosingcircle`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisminimumenclosingcircle`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4042
msgid "**Field**"
msgstr "**Polje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4047
msgid ""
"Features can be grouped by a field. If set, this causes the output layer to "
"contain one feature per grouped value with a minimal geometry covering only "
"the features with matching values."
msgstr ""
"Objekti se mogu grupisati po polju. Ako je postavljeno, ovo uzrokuje da "
"izlazni sloj sadrži po jedan objekat po grupisanoj vrednosti sa minimalnom "
"geometrijom koja pokriva samo objekte sa odgovarajućim vrednostima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4051
msgid "**Geometry type**"
msgstr "**Tip geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4056
msgid "Enclosing geometry types. One of:"
msgstr "Tipovi obuhvatajuće geometrije. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4058
msgid "0 --- Envelope (Bounding Box)"
msgstr "0 --- Omotnica (granični pravougaonik)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4059
msgid "1 --- Minimum Oriented Rectangle"
msgstr "1 --- Minimalni orijentisani pravougaonik"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4060
msgid "2 --- Minimum Enclosing Circle"
msgstr "2 --- Minimalni obuhvatajući krug"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4061
msgid "3 --- Convex Hull"
msgstr "3 --- Konveksni omotač"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4063
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4086
msgid "**Bounding geometry**"
msgstr "**Granična geometrija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4089
msgid ""
"The output (bounding) polygon vector layer. It has the fields from the input"
" layer and, depending on the selected parameter ``TYPE``, the output also "
"has the attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni (granični) poligonski vektorski sloj. Ima polja iz ulaznog sloja i, "
"u zavisnosti od izabranog parametra ``TYPE``, izlaz takođe ima atribute:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4094
msgid ""
"``width``, ``height``, ``area`` and ``perimeter`` of the Envelope (Bounding "
"Box)"
msgstr ""
"``width``, ``height``, ``area`` i ``perimeter`` omotnice (graničnog "
"pravougaonika)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4095
msgid ""
"``width``, ``height``, ``area``, ``angle`` and ``perimeter`` of the Minimum "
"Oriented Rectangle"
msgstr ""
"``width``, ``height``, ``area``, ``angle`` i ``perimeter`` minimalnog "
"orijentisanog pravougaonika"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4096
msgid "``radius`` and ``area`` of the Minimum Enclosing Circle"
msgstr "``radius`` i ``area`` minimalnog obuhvatajućeg kruga"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4097
msgid "``area`` and ``perimeter`` of the Convex Hull"
msgstr "``area`` i ``perimeter`` konveksnog omotača"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4102
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:minimumboundinggeometry``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:minimumboundinggeometry``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4112
msgid "Minimum enclosing circles"
msgstr "Minimalni obuhvatajući krugovi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4113
msgid ""
"Calculates the minimum enclosing circles of the features in the input layer."
msgstr "Računa minimalne obuhvatajuće krugove objekata u ulaznom sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4119
msgid "Enclosing circles for each feature"
msgstr "Obuhvatajući krugovi za svaki objekat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4143
msgid "**Number of segments in circles**"
msgstr "**Broj segmenata u krugovima**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4147
msgid "Default: 72"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 72"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4148
msgid ""
"The number of segments used to approximate a circle. Minimum 8, maximum "
"100000."
msgstr ""
"Broj segmenata koji se koristi za aproksimaciju kruga. Minimum 8, maksimum "
"100000."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4150
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4173
msgid "**Minimum enclosing circles**"
msgstr "**Minimalni obuhvatajući krugovi**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4176
msgid ""
"The output polygon vector layer. Other than the input attributes, the output"
" layer also contains the following fields: ``area`` and ``radius`` of the "
"generated polygon."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj. Pored ulaznih atributa, izlazni sloj "
"takođe sadrži sledeća polja: ``area`` i ``radius`` generisanog poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4184
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:minimumenclosingcircle``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:minimumenclosingcircle``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4194
msgid "Multi-ring buffer (constant distance)"
msgstr "Višeprstenasti bafer (konstantno rastojanje)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4195
msgid ""
"Computes multi-ring (*donut*) buffer for the features of the input layer, "
"using a fixed or dynamic distance and number of rings."
msgstr ""
"Računa višeprstenasti (*krofna*) bafer za objekte ulaznog sloja, koristeći "
"fiksno ili dinamičko rastojanje i broj prstenova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4201
msgid "Multi-ring buffer for a line, point and polygon layer"
msgstr "Višeprstenasti bafer za linijski, tačkasti i poligonski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4210
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisbuffer`, :ref:`qgisvariabledistancebuffer`, "
":ref:`qgisrectanglesovalsdiamonds`, :ref:`qgissinglesidedbuffer`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisbuffer`, :ref:`qgisvariabledistancebuffer`, "
":ref:`qgisrectanglesovalsdiamonds`, :ref:`qgissinglesidedbuffer`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4229
msgid "**Number of rings**"
msgstr "**Broj prstenova**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4230
msgid "``RINGS``"
msgstr "``RINGS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4234
msgid ""
"The number of rings. It can be a unique value (same number of rings for all "
"the features) or it can be taken from features data (the number of rings "
"depends on feature values)."
msgstr ""
"Broj prstenova. Može biti jedinstvena vrednost (isti broj prstenova za sve "
"objekte) ili se može uzeti iz podataka objekata (broj prstenova zavisi od "
"vrednosti objekata)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4238
msgid "**Distance between rings**"
msgstr "**Rastojanje između prstenova**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4243
msgid ""
"Distance between the rings. It can be a unique value (same distance for all "
"the features) or it can be taken from features data (the distance depends on"
" feature values)."
msgstr ""
"Rastojanje između prstenova. Može biti jedinstvena vrednost (isto rastojanje"
" za sve objekte) ili se može uzeti iz podataka objekata (rastojanje zavisi "
"od vrednosti objekata)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4247
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4270
msgid "**Multi-ring buffer (constant distance)**"
msgstr "**Višeprstenasti bafer (konstantno rastojanje)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4273
msgid ""
"The output polygon vector layer. Other than the input attributes, the output"
" layer also contains the following fields: ``ringId`` and ``distance`` of "
"the generated buffer polygon."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj. Pored ulaznih atributa, izlazni sloj "
"takođe sadrži sledeća polja: ``ringId`` i ``distance`` generisanog bafer "
"poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4280
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:multiringconstantbuffer``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:multiringconstantbuffer``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4290
msgid "Multipart to singleparts"
msgstr "Višedelno u jednodelno"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4291
msgid "Splits multipart features in the input layer into singlepart features."
msgstr "Deli višedelne objekte u ulaznom sloju na jednodelne objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4294
msgid ""
"The attributes of the output layer are the same as the original ones but "
"divided into single features."
msgstr ""
"Atributi izlaznog sloja su isti kao originalni, ali podeljeni na pojedinačne"
" objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4300
msgid ""
"Left the multipart source layer and right the single part output result"
msgstr "Levo višedelni izvorni sloj, a desno jednodelni izlazni rezultat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4312
msgid ":ref:`qgiscollect`, :ref:`qgispromotetomulti`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgiscollect`, :ref:`qgispromotetomulti`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4330
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4353
msgid "**Single parts**"
msgstr "**Jednodelni**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4356
msgid "The output vector layer."
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4361
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:multiparttosingleparts``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:multiparttosingleparts``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4371
msgid "Offset lines"
msgstr "Pomeri linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4372
msgid ""
"Offsets lines by a specified distance. Positive distances will offset lines "
"to the left, and negative distances will offset them to the right."
msgstr ""
"Odmiče linije za zadato rastojanje. Pozitivna rastojanja odmiču linije "
"ulevo, a negativna udesno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4379
msgid "In blue the source layer, in red the offset one"
msgstr "Plavo je izvorni sloj, crveno odmaknuti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4385
msgid ":ref:`qgisarrayoffsetlines`, :ref:`qgistranslategeometry`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisarrayoffsetlines`, :ref:`qgistranslategeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4409
msgid ""
"Offset distance. You can use the Data Defined button on the right to choose "
"a field from which the radius will be calculated. This way you can have "
"different radius for each feature (see :ref:`qgisvariabledistancebuffer`)."
msgstr ""
"Rastojanje pomeraja. Možete koristiti dugme Zamena definisana podacima sa "
"desne strane da biste izabrali polje iz kojeg će se izračunati poluprečnik. "
"Na ovaj način možete imati različit poluprečnik za svaki objekat (pogledajte"
" :ref:`qgisvariabledistancebuffer`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4418
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6416
msgid "Default: 8"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 8"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4459
msgid ""
"Specify the output (offset) layer. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni (pomereni) sloj. :ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4481
msgid "Output (offset) line layer"
msgstr "Izlazni (pomereni) linijski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4486
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:offsetline``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:offsetline``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4496
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4506
msgid "Oriented minimum bounding box"
msgstr "Orijentisani minimalni granični pravougaonik"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4497
msgid ""
"Calculates the minimum area rotated rectangle for each feature in the input "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"Računa rotirani pravougaonik minimalne površine za svaki objekat u ulaznom "
"sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4500
msgid ""
"For singlepart point features, the output corresponds to the bounding box of"
" the geometry."
msgstr ""
"Za jednodelne tačkaste objekte, izlaz odgovara graničnom pravougaoniku "
"geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4530
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4553
msgid "**Bounding boxes**"
msgstr "**Granični pravougaonici**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4556
msgid ""
"The output polygon vector layer. Other than the input attributes, the output"
" layer also contains the following fields: ``width``, ``height``, ``angle``,"
" ``area`` and ``perimeter`` of the generated polygon."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj. Pored ulaznih atributa, izlazni sloj "
"takođe sadrži sledeća polja: ``width``, ``height``, ``angle``, ``area`` i "
"``perimeter`` generisanog poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4564
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:orientedminimumboundingbox``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:orientedminimumboundingbox``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4574
msgid "Orthogonalize"
msgstr "Ortogonalizuj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4575
msgid ""
"Attempts to orthogonalize the geometries of the input line or polygon layer."
" This process shifts the vertices in the geometries to try to make every "
"angle in the geometry either a right angle or a straight line."
msgstr ""
"Pokušava da ortogonalizuje geometrije ulaznog linijskog ili poligonskog "
"sloja. Ovaj proces pomera temena u geometrijama da bi pokušao da svaki ugao "
"u geometriji učini ili pravim uglom ili pravom linijom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4583
msgid "In blue the source layer and in the red orthogonalized result"
msgstr "Plavom bojom izvorni sloj, a crvenom ortogonalizovani rezultat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4606
msgid "**Maximum angle tolerance (degrees)**"
msgstr "**Tolerancija maksimalnog ugla (stepeni)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4607
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4697
msgid "``ANGLE_TOLERANCE``"
msgstr "``ANGLE_TOLERANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4610
msgid "Default: 15.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 15.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4611
msgid ""
"Specify the maximum deviation from a right angle or straight line a vertex "
"can have for it to be adjusted. Smaller tolerances mean that only vertices "
"which are already closer to right angles will be adjusted, and larger "
"tolerances mean that vertices which deviate further from right angles will "
"also be adjusted."
msgstr ""
"Zadajte maksimalno odstupanje od pravog ugla ili prave linije koje teme može"
" imati da bi bilo prilagođeno. Manje tolerancije znače da će biti "
"prilagođena samo temena koja su već bliža pravim uglovima, a veće "
"tolerancije znače da će biti prilagođena i temena koja više odstupaju od "
"pravih uglova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4617
msgid "**Maximum algorithm iterations**"
msgstr "**Maksimalan broj iteracija algoritma**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4618
msgid "``MAX_ITERATIONS``"
msgstr "``MAX_ITERATIONS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4621
msgid "Default: 1000"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 1000"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4622
msgid ""
"Setting a larger number for the maximum number of iterations will result in "
"a more orthogonal geometry at the cost of extra processing time."
msgstr ""
"Postavljanje većeg broja za maksimalan broj iteracija daće ortogonalniju "
"geometriju uz cenu dodatnog vremena obrade."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4625
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4648
msgid "**Orthogonalized**"
msgstr "**Ortogonalizovano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4651
msgid "The output polygon vector layer with adjusted angles."
msgstr "Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj sa prilagođenim uglovima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4656
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:orthogonalize``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:orthogonalize``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4666
msgid "Point on Surface"
msgstr "Tačka na površini"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4667
msgid ""
"For each feature of the input layer, returns a point that is guaranteed to "
"lie on the surface of the feature geometry."
msgstr ""
"Za svaki objekat ulaznog sloja, vraća tačku za koju je zagarantovano da leži"
" na površini geometrije objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4678
msgid ":ref:`qgiscentroids`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgiscentroids`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4696
msgid "**Create point on surface for each part**"
msgstr "**Napravi tačku na površini za svaki deo**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4699
msgid "If checked, a point will be created for each part of the geometry."
msgstr "Ako je označeno, tačka će biti napravljena za svaki deo geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4700
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4723
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4963
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4986
msgid "**Point**"
msgstr "**Tačka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4705
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5197
msgid ""
"Specify the output point vector layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4726
msgid "The output point vector layer."
msgstr "Izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4731
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:pointonsurface``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:pointonsurface``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4741
msgid "Points along geometry"
msgstr "Tačke duž geometrije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4742
msgid ""
"Creates points at regular intervals along line or polygon geometries. "
"Created points will have new attributes added for the distance along the "
"geometry and the angle of the line at the point."
msgstr ""
"Pravi tačke u pravilnim intervalima duž geometrija linije ili poligona. "
"Napravljene tačke imaće dodata nova polja za rastojanje duž geometrije i "
"ugao linije na tački."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4746
msgid ""
"An optional start and end offset can be specified, which controls how far "
"from the start and end of the geometry the points should be created."
msgstr ""
"Može se zadati opcioni početni i krajnji pomeraj, koji kontroliše koliko "
"daleko od početka i kraja geometrije tačke treba da budu napravljene."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4753
msgid "Points created along the source line layer"
msgstr "Tačke napravljene duž izvornog linijskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4758
msgid ":ref:`qgisinterpolatepoint`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisinterpolatepoint`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4781
msgid "Distance between two consecutive points along the line"
msgstr "Rastojanje između dve uzastopne tačke duž linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4782
msgid "**Start offset**"
msgstr "**Početni pomeraj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4783
msgid "``START_OFFSET``"
msgstr "``START_OFFSET``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4787
msgid ""
"Distance from the beginning of the input line, representing the position of "
"the first point."
msgstr ""
"Rastojanje od početka ulazne linije, koje predstavlja položaj prve tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4789
msgid "**End offset**"
msgstr "**Krajnji pomeraj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4790
msgid "``END_OFFSET``"
msgstr "``END_OFFSET``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4794
msgid ""
"Distance from the end of the input line, representing the position beyond "
"which no point feature should be created."
msgstr ""
"Rastojanje od kraja ulazne linije, koje predstavlja položaj iza kojeg ne "
"treba praviti nijedan tačkasti objekat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4822
msgid ""
"Point vector layer with features placed along lines or polygon boundaries of"
" the input layer. Other than the input attributes on every related point, "
"the output layer also contains the following fields: ``distance`` and "
"``angle`` of the generated point."
msgstr ""
"Tačkasti vektorski sloj sa objektima postavljenim duž linija ili granica "
"poligona ulaznog sloja. Pored ulaznih atributa na svakoj povezanoj tački, "
"izlazni sloj takođe sadrži sledeća polja: ``distance`` i ``angle`` "
"generisane tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4831
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:pointsalonglines``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:pointsalonglines``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4841
msgid "Points displacement"
msgstr "Pomeranje tačaka"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4842
msgid ""
"Given a distance of proximity, identifies nearby point features and radially"
" distributes them over a circle whose center represents their barycenter. A "
"convenient tool to scatter overlaid features."
msgstr ""
"Za zadato rastojanje blizine, prepoznaje bliske tačkaste objekte i radijalno"
" ih raspoređuje po krugu čiji centar predstavlja njihov baricentar. Zgodna "
"alatka za rasipanje preklopljenih objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4863
msgid "**Minimum distance to other points**"
msgstr "**Minimalno rastojanje do drugih tačaka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4864
msgid "``PROXIMITY``"
msgstr "``PROXIMITY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4868
msgid ""
"Distance below which point features are considered close. Close features are"
" distributed altogether."
msgstr ""
"Rastojanje ispod kojeg se tačkasti objekti smatraju bliskim. Bliski objekti "
"se raspoređuju svi zajedno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4871
msgid "**Displacement distance**"
msgstr "**Rastojanje pomeranja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4876
msgid "Radius of the circle on which close features are placed"
msgstr "Poluprečnik kruga na koji se postavljaju bliski objekti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4877
msgid "**Horizontal distribution for two point case**"
msgstr "**Horizontalna raspodela za slučaj dve tačke**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4878
msgid "``HORIZONTAL``"
msgstr "``HORIZONTAL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4882
msgid ""
"When only two points are identified as close, aligns them horizontally on "
"the circle instead of vertically."
msgstr ""
"Kada su samo dve tačke prepoznate kao bliske, poravnava ih horizontalno na "
"krugu umesto vertikalno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4885
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4908
msgid "**Displaced**"
msgstr "**Pomereno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4911
msgid "Output point vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4916
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:pointsdisplacement``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:pointsdisplacement``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4926
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4939
msgid "Pole of inaccessibility"
msgstr "Pol nepristupačnosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4927
msgid ""
"Calculates the pole of inaccessibility for a polygon layer, which is the "
"most distant internal point from the boundary of the surface."
msgstr ""
"Računa pol nepristupačnosti za poligonski sloj, što je najudaljenija "
"unutrašnja tačka od granice površine."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4930
msgid ""
"This algorithm uses the 'polylabel' algorithm (Vladimir Agafonkin, 2016), "
"which is an iterative approach guaranteed to find the true pole of "
"inaccessibility within a specified tolerance. A more precise tolerance "
"(lower value) requires more iterations and will take longer to calculate."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam koristi algoritam „polylabel“ (Vladimir Agafonkin, 2016), "
"koji je iterativni pristup zagarantovan da pronađe pravi pol "
"nepristupačnosti unutar zadate tolerancije. Preciznija tolerancija (niža "
"vrednost) zahteva više iteracija i trajaće duže da se izračuna."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4962
msgid "Set the tolerance for the calculation"
msgstr "Postavite toleranciju za izračunavanje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4989
msgid ""
"The output point vector layer. It will contain a new attribute with the "
"distance ``dist_pole`` from the calculated pole to the polygon boundary."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj. Sadržaće novi atribut sa rastojanjem "
"``dist_pole`` od izračunatog pola do granice poligona."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4996
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:poleofinaccessibility``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:poleofinaccessibility``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5006
msgid "Polygonize"
msgstr "Poligonizuj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5007
msgid ""
"Creates a polygon layer whose features boundaries are generated from a line "
"layer of **closed** features."
msgstr ""
"Pravi poligonski sloj čije se granice objekata generišu iz linijskog sloja "
"**zatvorenih** objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5013
msgid "The yellow polygons generated from the closed lines"
msgstr "Žuti poligoni generisani iz zatvorenih linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5015
msgid ""
"The line layer must have closed shapes in order to be transformed into a "
"polygon."
msgstr ""
"Linijski sloj mora imati zatvorene oblike da bi bio transformisan u poligon."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5018
msgid ""
":ref:`qgispolygonstolines`, :ref:`qgislinestopolygons`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgispolygonstolines`, :ref:`qgislinestopolygons`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5036
msgid "**Keep fields from the input layer**"
msgstr "**Zadrži polja iz ulaznog sloja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5037
msgid "``KEEP_FIELDS``"
msgstr "``KEEP_FIELDS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5041
msgid ""
"Check to keep the fields (only the table structure, not the values) of the "
"input layer"
msgstr ""
"Označite da biste zadržali polja (samo strukturu tabele, ne vrednosti) "
"ulaznog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5042
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5065
msgid "**Polygons from lines**"
msgstr "**Poligoni iz linija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5068
msgid "The output polygon vector layer from lines"
msgstr "Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj iz linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5074
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:polygonize``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:polygonize``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5084
msgid "Polygons to lines"
msgstr "Poligoni u linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5085
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon layer and creates a line layer, with lines representing the "
"boundaries of the polygons in the input layer."
msgstr ""
"Uzima poligonski sloj i pravi linijski sloj, sa linijama koje predstavljaju "
"granice poligona u ulaznom sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5094
msgid "Black lines as the result of the algorithm"
msgstr "Crne linije kao rezultat algoritma"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5098
msgid ""
":ref:`qgislinestopolygons`, :ref:`qgispolygonize`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgislinestopolygons`, :ref:`qgispolygonize`, "
":ref:`qgisconvertgeometrytype`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5116
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5139
msgid "**Lines**"
msgstr "**Linije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5142
msgid "The output line vector layer from polygons"
msgstr "Izlazni linijski vektorski sloj iz poligona"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5147
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:polygonstolines``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:polygonstolines``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5157
msgid "Project points (Cartesian)"
msgstr "Projektuj tačke (kartezijanski)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5158
msgid ""
"Projects point geometries by a specified distance and bearing (azimuth)."
msgstr "Projektuje geometrije tačaka za zadato rastojanje i smer (azimut)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5180
msgid "**Bearing (degrees from North)**"
msgstr "**Smer (stepeni od severa)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5181
msgid "``BEARING``"
msgstr "``BEARING``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5185
msgid "Clockwise angle starting from North, in degree (°) unit"
msgstr "Ugao u smeru kazaljke na satu počev od severa, u jedinici stepeni (°)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5191
msgid "Distance to offset geometries, in layer units"
msgstr "Rastojanje za pomeraj geometrija, u jedinicama sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5192
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5215
msgid "**Projected**"
msgstr "**Projektovano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5218
msgid "The output (projected) point vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni (projektovani) tačkasti vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5223
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:projectpointcartesian``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:projectpointcartesian``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5233
msgid "Promote to multipart"
msgstr "Unapredi u višedelno"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5234
msgid ""
"Takes a vector layer with singlepart geometries and generates a new one in "
"which all geometries are multipart."
msgstr ""
"Uzima vektorski sloj sa jednodelnim geometrijama i generiše novi u kojem su "
"sve geometrije višedelne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5237
msgid ""
"Input features which are already multipart features will remain unchanged."
msgstr "Ulazni objekti koji su već višedelni objekti ostaće nepromenjeni."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5240
msgid ""
"This algorithm can be used to force geometries to multipart types in order "
"to be compatible with data providers that require multipart features."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam se može koristiti za prisiljavanje geometrija na višedelne "
"tipove radi kompatibilnosti sa provajderima podataka koji zahtevaju "
"višedelne objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5248
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisaggregate`, :ref:`qgiscollect`, :ref:`qgisfixgeometrymultipart`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisaggregate`, :ref:`qgiscollect`, :ref:`qgisfixgeometrymultipart`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5267
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5290
msgid "**Multiparts**"
msgstr "**Višedelni**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5272
msgid ""
"Specify the output multipart vector layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni višedelni vektorski sloj. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5293
msgid "The output multipart vector layer"
msgstr "Izlazni višedelni vektorski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5298
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:promotetomulti``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:promotetomulti``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5308
msgid "Rectangles, ovals, diamonds"
msgstr "Pravougaonici, ovali, rombovi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5309
msgid ""
"Creates a buffer area with a rectangle, oval or diamond shape for each "
"feature of the input point layer."
msgstr ""
"Pravi oblast bafera oblika pravougaonika, ovala ili romba za svaki objekat "
"ulaznog tačkastog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5312
msgid ""
"The shape parameters can be fixed for all features or dynamic using a field "
"or an expression."
msgstr ""
"Parametri oblika mogu biti fiksni za sve objekte ili dinamički pomoću polja "
"ili izraza."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5318
msgid "Different buffer shapes with dynamic parameters"
msgstr "Različiti oblici bafera sa dinamičkim parametrima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5336
msgid "**Buffer shape**"
msgstr "**Oblik bafera**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5337
msgid "``SHAPE``"
msgstr "``SHAPE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5339
msgid "The shape to use. One of:"
msgstr "Oblik koji se koristi. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5341
msgid "0 --- Rectangles"
msgstr "0 --- Pravougaonici"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5342
msgid "1 --- Ovals"
msgstr "1 --- Ovali"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5343
msgid "2 --- Diamonds"
msgstr "2 --- Rombovi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5345
msgid "**Width**"
msgstr "**Širina**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5350
msgid "Width of the buffer shape"
msgstr "Širina oblika bafera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5351
msgid "**Height**"
msgstr "**Visina**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5352
msgid "``HEIGHT``"
msgstr "``HEIGHT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5356
msgid "Height of the buffer shape"
msgstr "Visina oblika bafera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5357
msgid "**Rotation**"
msgstr "**Rotacija**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5360
msgid "``ROTATION``"
msgstr "``ROTATION``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5364
msgid "Rotation of the buffer shape"
msgstr "Rotacija oblika bafera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5365
msgid "**Number of segments**"
msgstr "**Broj segmenata**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5369
msgid "Default: 36"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 36"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5370
msgid "Number of segments for a full circle (*Ovals* shape)"
msgstr "Broj segmenata za pun krug (oblik *Ovali*)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5371
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5394
msgid "**Output**"
msgstr "**Izlaz**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5397
msgid "The output vector layer (with the buffer shapes)"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj (sa oblicima bafera)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5402
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rectanglesovalsdiamonds``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:rectanglesovalsdiamonds``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5412
msgid "Remove duplicate vertices"
msgstr "Ukloni duplirana temena"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5413
msgid ""
"Removes duplicate vertices from features, wherever removing the vertices "
"does not result in a degenerate geometry."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja duplirana temena iz objekata, svuda gde uklanjanje temena ne "
"rezultira degenerisanom geometrijom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5416
msgid ""
"The tolerance parameter specifies the tolerance for coordinates when "
"determining whether vertices are identical."
msgstr ""
"Parametar tolerancije zadaje toleranciju za koordinate pri određivanju da li"
" su temena identična."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5419
msgid ""
"By default, Z values are not considered when detecting duplicate vertices. "
"E.g. two vertices with the same X and Y coordinate but different Z values "
"will still be considered duplicate and one will be removed. If the "
":guilabel:`Use Z Value` parameter is true, then the Z values are also tested"
" and vertices with the same X and Y but different Z will be maintained."
msgstr ""
"Podrazumevano se Z vrednosti ne uzimaju u obzir pri otkrivanju dupliranih "
"temena. Npr. dva temena sa istom X i Y koordinatom, ali različitim Z "
"vrednostima i dalje će se smatrati dupliranim i jedno će biti uklonjeno. Ako"
" je parametar :guilabel:`Koristi Z vrednost` tačan, tada se testiraju i Z "
"vrednosti, a temena sa istim X i Y, ali različitim Z biće zadržana."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5430
msgid ""
"Duplicate vertices are not tested between different parts of a multipart "
"geometry, e.g. a multipoint geometry with overlapping points will not be "
"changed by this method."
msgstr ""
"Duplirana temena se ne testiraju između različitih delova višedelne "
"geometrije, npr. višetačkasta geometrija sa preklapajućim tačkama neće biti "
"promenjena ovim metodom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5434
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisextractvertices`, :ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisdeleteduplicategeometries`, :ref:`qgisfixgeometryduplicatenodes`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisextractvertices`, :ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisdeleteduplicategeometries`, :ref:`qgisfixgeometryduplicatenodes`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5460
msgid "Vertices closer than the specified distance are considered duplicates"
msgstr "Temena bliža od zadatog rastojanja smatraju se duplikatima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5462
msgid "**Use Z value**"
msgstr "**Koristi Z vrednost**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5463
msgid "``USE_Z_VALUE``"
msgstr "``USE_Z_VALUE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5467
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Use Z Value` parameter is true, then the Z values are also"
" tested and vertices with the same X and Y but different Z will be "
"maintained."
msgstr ""
"Ako je parametar :guilabel:`Koristi Z vrednost` tačan, tada se testiraju i Z"
" vrednosti, a temena sa istim X i Y, ali različitim Z biće zadržana."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5496
msgid "The output vector layer (without duplicate vertices)"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj (bez dupliranih temena)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5501
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:removeduplicatevertices``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:removeduplicatevertices``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5511
msgid "Remove null geometries"
msgstr "Ukloni nulte geometrije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5513
msgid ""
"Removes any features which do not have a geometry from a vector layer. All "
"other features will be copied unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja sve objekte koji nemaju geometriju iz vektorskog sloja. Svi ostali "
"objekti biće kopirani nepromenjeni."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5516
msgid "The features with null geometries can be saved to a separate layer."
msgstr "Objekti sa nultim geometrijama mogu se sačuvati u zaseban sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5518
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Also remove empty geometries` is checked, the algorithm "
"removes features whose geometries have no coordinates, i.e., geometries that"
" are empty. In that case, also the null output will reflect this option, "
"containing both null and empty geometries."
msgstr ""
"Ako je označeno :guilabel:`Ukloni i prazne geometrije`, algoritam uklanja "
"objekte čije geometrije nemaju koordinate, tj. geometrije koje su prazne. U "
"tom slučaju, i nulti izlaz će odražavati ovu opciju, sadržeći i nulte i "
"prazne geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5524
msgid ":ref:`qgisdeleteduplicategeometries`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdeleteduplicategeometries`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5541
msgid "Input vector layer (with non-NULL geometries)"
msgstr "Ulazni vektorski sloj (sa ne-NULL geometrijama)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5542
msgid "**Also remove empty geometries**"
msgstr "**Ukloni i prazne geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5543
msgid "``REMOVE_EMPTY``"
msgstr "``REMOVE_EMPTY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5546
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5591
msgid "**Non null geometries**"
msgstr "**Ne-nulte geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5553
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer for the non-NULL (and non-empty) geometries."
" :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj za ne-NULL (i neprazne) geometrije. "
":ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5561
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5587
msgid "**Null geometries**"
msgstr "**Nulte geometrije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5564
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5588
msgid "``NULL_OUTPUT``"
msgstr "``NULL_OUTPUT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5567
msgid "Default: ``[Skip output]``"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: ``[Skip output]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5568
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer for the NULL (and empty) geometries. "
":ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj za NULL (i prazne) geometrije. :ref:`Jedno od"
" <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5590
msgid "Output vector layer (for NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni vektorski sloj (za NULL i, ako je izabrano, prazne geometrije)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5594
msgid ""
"The output vector layer (without NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni vektorski sloj (bez NULL i, ako je izabrano, praznih geometrija)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5599
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:removenullgeometries``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:removenullgeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5609
msgid "Reverse line direction"
msgstr "Obrni smer linije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5610
msgid "Inverts the direction of a line layer."
msgstr "Invertuje smer linijskog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5615
msgid "Before and after the direction inversion"
msgstr "Pre i posle inverzije smera"

