msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:rotatefeatures``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5764
msgid "Roundness"
msgstr "Zaobljenost"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5766
msgid ""
"Calculates the roundness of each feature and stores it as a new field "
"``roundness``. The input vector layer must contain polygons."
msgstr ""
"Računa zaobljenost svakog objekta i čuva je kao novo polje ``roundness``. "
"Ulazni vektorski sloj mora sadržati poligone."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5768
msgid ""
"The roundness of a polygon is defined as 4π × polygon area / perimeter². The"
" roundness value varies between 0 and 1. A perfect circle has a roundness of"
" 1, while a completely flat polygon has a roundness of 0."
msgstr ""
"Zaobljenost poligona definiše se kao 4π × površina poligona / obim². "
"Vrednost zaobljenosti varira između 0 i 1. Savršen krug ima zaobljenost 1, "
"dok potpuno ravan poligon ima zaobljenost 0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5772
msgid "The algorithm returns NULL for multipart polygon features."
msgstr "Algoritam vraća NULL za višedelne poligonske objekte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5795
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5819
msgid "**Roundness**"
msgstr "**Zaobljenost**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5800
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer (with roundness field). :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj (sa poljem zaobljenosti). :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5822
msgid "The output vector layer with ``roundness`` value in a field"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa ``roundness`` vrednošću u polju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5827
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:roundness``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:roundness``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5837
msgid "Segmentize by maximum angle"
msgstr "Segmentizuj po maksimalnom uglu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5838
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5916
msgid ""
"Segmentizes a geometry by converting curved sections to linear sections."
msgstr ""
"Segmentizuje geometriju pretvaranjem zakrivljenih delova u linearne delove."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5841
msgid ""
"The segmentization is performed by specifying the maximum allowed radius "
"angle between vertices on the straightened geometry (e.g the angle of the "
"arc created from the original arc center to consecutive output vertices on "
"the linearized geometry). Non-curved geometries will be retained without "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Segmentizacija se vrši zadavanjem maksimalnog dozvoljenog ugla poluprečnika "
"između temena na ispravljenoj geometriji (npr. ugla luka napravljenog od "
"centra originalnog luka do uzastopnih izlaznih temena na linearizovanoj "
"geometriji). Nezakrivljene geometrije biće zadržane bez izmene."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5847
msgid ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5866
msgid "**Maximum angle between vertices (degrees)**"
msgstr "**Maksimalni ugao između temena (stepeni)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5870
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7301
msgid "Default: 5.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 5.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5871
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed radius angle between vertices on the straightened geometry"
msgstr ""
"Maksimalni dozvoljeni ugao poluprečnika između temena na ispravljenoj "
"geometriji"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5873
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5897
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5951
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5975
msgid "**Segmentized**"
msgstr "**Segmentizovano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5878
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5956
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer (with segmentized geometries). :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj (sa segmentizovanim geometrijama). "
":ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5900
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5978
msgid "The output vector layer with segmentized geometries"
msgstr "Izlazni vektorski sloj sa segmentizovanim geometrijama"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5905
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxangle``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:segmentizebymaxangle``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5915
msgid "Segmentize by maximum distance"
msgstr "Segmentizuj po maksimalnom rastojanju"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5919
msgid ""
"The segmentization is performed by specifying the maximum allowed offset "
"distance between the original curve and the segmentized representation. Non-"
"curved geometries will be retained without change."
msgstr ""
"Segmentizacija se vrši zadavanjem maksimalnog dozvoljenog rastojanja "
"pomeraja između originalne krive i segmentizovane reprezentacije. "
"Nezakrivljene geometrije biće zadržane bez izmene."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5924
msgid ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxangle`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxangle`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5943
msgid "**Maximum offset distance**"
msgstr "**Maksimalno rastojanje pomeraja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5948
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed offset distance between the original curve and the "
"segmentized representation, in the layer units."
msgstr ""
"Maksimalno dozvoljeno rastojanje pomeraja između originalne krive i "
"segmentizovane reprezentacije, u jedinicama sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5983
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxdistance``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:segmentizebymaxdistance``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5993
msgid "Set M value"
msgstr "Postavi M vrednost"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5994
msgid "Sets the M value for geometries in a layer."
msgstr "Postavlja M vrednost za geometrije u sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5996
msgid ""
"If M values already exist in the layer, they will be overwritten with the "
"new value. If no M values exist, the geometry will be upgraded to include M "
"values and the specified value used as the initial M value for all "
"geometries."
msgstr ""
"Ako M vrednosti već postoje u sloju, biće prepisane novom vrednošću. Ako M "
"vrednosti ne postoje, geometrija će biti unapređena da uključi M vrednosti, "
"a zadata vrednost se koristi kao početna M vrednost za sve geometrije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6002
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6089
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line, and polygon features with M "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste, linijske i poligonske objekte sa "
"omogućenim M"

