msgstr "**Kopiraj atribute iz ulaznih objekata**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7590
msgid "``COPY_ATTRIBUTES``"
msgstr "``COPY_ATTRIBUTES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7594
msgid ""
"Specifies whether fields storing involved point features ID should be added "
"to the output. If False, an ``id`` field is created to identify the "
"polygons."
msgstr ""
"Zadaje da li treba dodati polja koja čuvaju ID uključenih tačkastih objekata"
" u izlaz. Ako je False, pravi se ``id`` polje za identifikaciju poligona."

